<i>noun</i>: 해빙 [해ː빙], 용해 [용해] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>해빙 [해ː빙]</dt><br>
<dd>1. thawing; melting</dd><br>
<dd>얼음이 녹음.</dd><br>
<dd>The melting of ice.</dd><br>
<dd>2. thawing; melting</dd><br>
<dd>(비유적으로) 서로 대립 중이던 집단이나 나라 사이의 긴장이 느슨해짐.</dd><br>
<dd>(figurative) The easing of tension between two opposing groups or countries.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>용해 [용해]</dt><br>
<dd>melting; dissolution</dd><br>
<dd>녹거나 녹이는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>The process of fusing something or being fused.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>